Package: diffr
Type: Package
Version: 0.1
Title: Normalization and difference calling for Next Generation Sequencing
    (NGS) data via joint multinomial modeling.
Description: diffr implements normalization and diff calling procedures for NGS
    data. Two NGS experiments are jointly modeled as a multinomial sampling
    trial.
Date: 2014-12-18
Author: Johannes Helmuth
Maintainer: Johannes Helmuth <helmuth@molgen.mpg.de>
Depends: 
    Rcpp (>= 0.11.3)
Imports: 
    bamsignals,
    GenomeInfoDb,
    GenomicRanges,
    IRanges,
    parallel
Suggests: 
    ggplot2,
	optparse,
    testthat (>= 0.9),
    knitr
LinkingTo: Rcpp
License: GPL-3
VignetteBuilder: knitr
